file.name: duplicate-fields.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  title: Simple
paths:
  /pets:
    patch:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Updated
components:
  schemas:
    Test:
      type: object
      properties:
        x:
          type: string
    Test2:
      # duplicate fields will be replaced based on type order
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Test"
        - type: object
          properties:
            x:
              type: number
